snippet.title: Boomerang Fu - Release Date Trailer - Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
Slice and dice your friends with boomerangs in this frantic physics party game for up to 6 players. Coming to Nintendo Switch on August 13th, 2020. Learn more: http://boomerangfu.com
